{"tid":34221,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"深水步文昌雞飯","createTime":"2016-12-11T10:56:16.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T10:12:46.000Z","uid":62277,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f6c12a9a17cadd668326ae39df5d4c026b49d83","tid":34221,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T10:56:16.000Z","msg":"係香港主要食到既都係冰鮮雞<br />\n難得呢度雞味十足,皮又算薄<br />\n雖然唔稱得上好嫩滑<br />\n但肉有彈性,唔會un<br />\n個汁酸酸辣辣之餘,帶有蒜香,食落好開胃<br />\n<br />\n另有海南雞飯供應<br />\n不過水準一般<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔是油飯,是黃薑飯<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mcgo0419\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmcgo0419&h=4255fe34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lzsjerd4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flzsjerd4&h=4bd921c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b83e90700272855d1fc5af73a8f9d5a0e9f2ff92","tid":34221,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T10:57:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76958c07289af4d74cd0c335538f94ff441c4544","tid":34221,"uid":39780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T10:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228476f8c385d2ba8a99e19f180af1cae5ed1776","tid":34221,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T10:59:01.000Z","msg":"幾似泰式海南雞飯"},{"pid":"4954e0e6329d84642cc3a607f1af52a0cc53c9b9","tid":34221,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n地址？"},{"pid":"92652976c9ee10458462689c24776dfa2289035c","tid":34221,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:20:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾似泰式海南雞飯</blockquote><b