cf9042d472cad462fe","tid":34221,"uid":17123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:06:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中出過咗嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n終於冇人盲目咁話你打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好的開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccffab8c89d51b8b8c34762e03707ec6f0dc6236","tid":34221,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:40:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主<br />\n呢度打到<span style=\"color: blue;\">埗</span>字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nok,thx"},{"pid":"fb5bb2101d8ee4fb5fc5888b46f3222c78476f83","tid":34221,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中出過咗嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n終於冇人盲目咁話你打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感覺上呢邊少d mk仔同高登食家"},{"pid":"1b688e597090e2a1f87ed7ed38466e130c9c4d12","tid":34221,"uid":7230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:42:28.000Z","msg":"得個五嚿<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b51ac954b5ec1ac5469f9155b2482b81e08641","tid":34221,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:50:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽日去試下<br />\n唔知到時會唔會排長龍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同金雞比 邊個高汁啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然一個海南雞 一個文昌雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早兩日去食大圍漢年<br />\n啲雞甩皮甩骨 質素好唔穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n漢年好麻麻,大埔嘉華都仲比佢好<br />\n要嫩滑就屯門文聚<br />\n要雞味就呢度<br />\n要兩樣都有,可以去鰂魚涌津津(轉肶+併雞肝)<br />\n<br />\n海南雞以前大古城三巡好正,而家執左<br />\n可試下mk新世紀food court分店,(<br />\n大概有太古分店8成水準(間間分店水準有差異)<br />\n,我會跟餐走翼<br />\nopenrice無資料,可上去望望<br />\n<br />\n金雞未試過"},{"pid":"d123cf8fa1fd43d3275c54691ec616afc4f60f90","tid":34221,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:53:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得個五嚿<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有舊肶尾"},{"pid":"d65b85eabe9d1d22552844a2a6626a3c03999126","tid":34221,"uid":17123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:09:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同金雞比 邊個高汁啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然一個海南雞 一個文昌雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早兩日去食大圍漢年<br />\n啲雞甩皮甩骨 質素好唔穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n漢年好麻麻,大埔嘉華都仲比佢好<br />\n要嫩滑就屯門文聚<br />\n要雞味就呢度<br />\n要兩樣都有,可以去鰂魚涌津津(轉肶+併雞肝)<br />\n<br />\n海南雞以前大古城三巡好正,而家執左<br />\n可試下mk新世紀food court分店,(<br />\n大概有太古分店8成水準(間間分店水準有差異)<br />\n,我會跟餐走翼<br />\nopenrice無資料,可上去望望<br />\n<br />\n金雞未試過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n漢年仲要斬翼比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我話走胸 佢就比翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前 老闆娘認得會比我打尖<br />\n又會斬脾位比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲要好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家小去 人又肥咗兩個碼 入到去連招呼都冇打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw得閒試吓三巡先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外新寶戲院隔離間泰妃雞都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上個禮拜食又一城大家樂個海南雞都有驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過好早就賣晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6f2eccf839171c90c2022ee24a599ed7242a8c","tid":34221,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:12:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同金雞比 邊個高汁啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然一個海南雞 一個文昌雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早兩日去食大圍漢年<br />\n啲雞甩皮甩骨 質素好唔穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n漢年好麻麻,大埔嘉華都仲比佢好<br />\n要嫩滑就屯門文聚<br />\n要雞味就呢度<br />\n要兩樣都有,可以去鰂魚涌津津(轉肶+併雞肝)<br />\n<br />\n海南雞以前大古城三巡好正,而家執左<br />\n可試下mk新世紀food court分店,(<br />\n大概有太古分店8成水準(間間分店水準有差異)<br />\n,我會跟餐走翼<br />\nopenrice無資料,可上去望望<br />\n<br />\n金雞未試過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n漢年仲要斬翼比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我話走胸 佢就比翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前 老闆娘認得會比我打尖<br />\n又會斬脾位比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲要好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家小去 人又肥咗兩個碼 入到去連招呼都冇打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw得閒試吓三巡先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外新寶戲院隔離間泰妃雞都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上個禮拜食又一城大家樂個海南雞都有驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過好早就賣晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泰妃雞食過一次<br />\n唔多啱我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}